WEBVTT

00:00:27.219 --> 00:00:30.859
I thought I would spend
my entire life in North Korea,

00:00:30.883 --> 00:00:33.267
until everything suddenly changed.

00:00:34.587 --> 00:00:39.108
When I was seven years old,
I saw my first public execution.

00:00:39.584 --> 00:00:42.200
But I thought my life
in North Korea was normal.

00:00:42.779 --> 00:00:44.693
My family was not poor,

00:00:44.717 --> 00:00:47.946
and myself, I had never
experienced hunger.

00:00:48.414 --> 00:00:52.955
But one day, in 1995,
my mom brought home a letter

00:00:52.979 --> 00:00:54.979
from a coworker's sister.

00:00:55.003 --> 00:00:58.014
It read, "When you read this,

00:00:58.038 --> 00:01:02.870
our five family members
